Text:
As the first comment here, I'd like to commend you for not hardsubbing your SWESUB release here. It attracts seeders. 
It would help if you provided: Framerate, compression codec, bitrates and an english description.
This is just constructive critique though, good job with this!

V: 8/10 where 10 is true 1080p
A: 9/10
M: Overall 7/10, Fight scenes 10/10

Nice rip.
